                        <interp inst="t18380917-name-241" type="given" value="JANE"></interp>JANE DYER</persName>
                  </hi>. I live with my father, Edward Dyer, who keeps the Rock public-house, Lisson-grove. On the 4th of September I was on the leads at the back of the house, and saw the prisoner come out of the back kitchen down wash the lid of the copper boiler, which had been in the kitchen—I told my father.</p>
